description: When the single parents of hot teens Calvin Banks and Troy Accola decide to get married, the two young men are asked to regard each other as brothers. Gorgeous, self-assured Calvin quickly gets the upper hand over shy, self-conscious Troy, and soon tensions begin to mount between the two hung young studs. When Troy walks in on Calvin having sex with sexy Andrew Fitch, the frustrated teen decides he can take no more. But does Troy's rage mask an overwhelming attraction for his new brother? Written and directed by Nica Noelle.
title: Time To Try A Real Man Scene 3
